se over 65 years 20.7\% versus 25.4\% ({OR} = 0.99, 95\% {CI} = 0.96 to 1.02).{\textbar}Practices where primary care teams received an educational outreach visit demonstrated a significantly greater improvement in uptake in high-risk groups for pneumococcal but not influenza vaccine.},
