nd {ICD}-9-{CM} co-morbidity coding algorithms produce similar estimates of comorbidity prevalence in administrative data, and may outperform existing {ICD}-9-{CM} coding algorithms. Copyright © 2005 by Lippincott Williams \& Wilkins.},
